<user_query>
The texts in the buttons are at the center. But I want them at the extreme left of the button
</user_query>"}]},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To align the button texts to the extreme left (start) inside each button, you need to:
- Set the button content to fill the width.
- Align the `Text` composable to `Alignment.Start` within the button.

In Jetpack Compose, you achieve this by wrapping the text in a `Row`:
- Set `Modifier.fillMaxWidth()` on the `Row`.
- Set `horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.Start`.
